kin-office (1.0.9-1) stable; urgency=high

  * direct-connector: rewrite loopback Document Server save URLs to internal
    document editor service (fixes callback download failures); only set save_pending when
    forcesave is accepted.
  * office apps: on editor "saved", force-save and sync to Kin when callback
    is slow; show Save failed dialog instead of silent log only.

